l-news/2023-12-08/ty-article/.premium/palestinian-pm-working-with-u-s-on-day-after-plan-which-must-include-hamas/0000018c-4851-db23-ad9f-68d94e850000</guid></item><item><title>如果以色列部长甘茨决定支持内塔尼亚胡的战争政府，他的政党将面临分裂</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-08/ty-article/.premium/israeli-party-faces-split-if-gantzs-faction-decides-to-bolt-netanyahus-war-time/0000018c-45f5-db23-ad9f-6dfdcc680000</link><description>如果甘茨领导的卡霍尔·拉文党退出，以吉迪恩·萨尔为首的新希望派选择留在政府，民族团结党可能会分崩离析</description><pubDate>Fri, 08 Dec 2023 04:00:24 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-08/ty-article/.premium/israeli-party-faces-split-if-gantzs-faction-decides-to-bolt-netanyahus-war-time/0000018c-45f5-db23-ad9f-6dfdcc680000</guid></item><item><title>哈马斯无法阻止以色列军队——但辛瓦尔有其他计划</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-08/ty-article/.premium/hamas-cant-hold-the-israeli-army-back-but-sinwar-has-other-plans/0000018c-45da-db23-ad9f-6ddae6ca0000</link><description>加沙的以色列军队正在努力保住他们所占领的领土 ■ 哈马斯领导人已经实现了他们梦想的一切，正在隧道里等待美国告诉以色列，时间到了</description><pubDate>Fri, 08 Dec 2023 04:00:19 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-08/ty-article/.premium/hamas-cant-hold-the-israeli-army-back-but-sinwar-has-other-plans/0000018c-45da-db23-ad9f-6ddae6ca0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列人质的家人破解了内塔尼亚胡密码并获得了一剂有毒的比比主义</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-08/ty-article/.premium/families-of-israeli-hostages-crack-the-netanyahu-code-and-get-a-dose-of-toxic-bibi-ism/0000018c-45cd-db80-afbd-cfffae590000</link><description>只有当人质家人威胁要去找拜登总统时，以色列总理才同意会见他们 ■ 战争两个月后，以色列领导人又回到了他们的坏习惯——再次承诺拆除、推翻、摧毁和根除哈马斯</description><pubDate>Fri, 08 Dec 2023 04:00:12 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-08/ty-article/.premium/families-of-israeli-hostages-crack-the-netanyahu-code-and-get-a-dose-of-toxic-bibi-ism/0000018c-45cd-db80-afbd-cfffae590000</guid></item><item><title>两名以色列国防军士兵在加沙战斗中丧生；六名巴勒斯坦人在约旦河西岸冲突中丧生</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-08/ty-article-live/israel-to-open-kerem-shalom-crossing-u-s-no-deadline-on-idf-to-end-gaza-war/0000018c-4779-db23-ad9f-6ff9873e0000</link><description>两名预备役军人在加沙战斗中丧生 ■ 以色列国防军：过去一天在加沙袭击了 450 个目标，部队袭击了试图发射火箭弹的恐怖小队 ■ 陆军发言人称，以色列国防军连夜袭击了黎巴嫩的牢房和叙利亚的目标 ■ 以色列同意开放凯雷姆沙洛姆过境点美国高级官员表示，仅供检查之用 ■ 自 10 月 7 日以来，以色列至少有 1,200 名平民和士兵被杀；超过 138 名人质仍被扣押在加沙 ■ 哈马斯卫生部：17,177 人死亡，46,000 人受伤</description><pubDate>Fri, 08 Dec 2023 03:36:21 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-08/ty-article-live/israel-to-open-kerem-shalom-crossing-u-s-no-deadline-on-idf-to-end-gaza-war/0000018c-4779-db23-ad9f-6ff9873e0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列确认了德罗尔·卡普伦 (Dror Kaplun) 的遗骸，据信他是在加沙被扣押的人质之一</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-08/ty-article/.premium/israel-identifies-remains-of-dror-kaplun-thought-to-have-been-among-hostages-held-in-gaza/0000018c-4691-db80-afbd-cffb118e0000</link><description>贝埃里基布兹居民的妻子在 10 月 7 日的大屠杀中被杀，据信已被哈马斯绑架</description><pubDate>Thu, 07 Dec 2023 23:24:49 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-08/ty-article/.premium/israel-identifies-remains-of-dror-kaplun-thought-to-have-been-among-hostages-held-in-gaza/0000018c-4691-db80-afbd-cffb118e0000</guid></item><item><title>“不知何故，恐怖分子忽略了我的儿子。他们损坏了一切，却错过了他”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/holylandings/2023-12-08/ty-article/.highlight/somehow-the-terrorists-skipped-my-son-they-damaged-everything-but-missed-him/0000018c-4667-db23-ad9f-6efffd150000</link><description>本周在本古里安机场：一位美国妈妈来到以色列看望她在军队服役并在哈马斯袭击中幸存的儿子；一个受到 10 月 7 日悲剧影响的家庭前往雅典短暂休息</description><pubDate>Thu, 07 Dec 2023 22:55:55 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/holylandings/2023-12-08/ty-article/.highlight/somehow-the-terrorists-skipped-my-son-they-damaged-everything-but-missed-him/0000018c-4667-db23-ad9f-6efffd150000</guid></item><item><title>以色列对加沙的单边战略将继续导致灾难</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-08/ty-article-opinion/.highlight/israels-unilateral-strategy-toward-gaza-will-keep-leading-to-disaster/0000018c-4507-d6bd-a1ad-7fd7ad320000</link><description>以色列 2005 年从加沙撤军是导致 10 月 7 日灾难的一个重要节点。 回应 Adam Raz</description><pubDate>Thu, 07 Dec 2023 22:29:30 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-08/ty-article-opinion/.highlight/israels-unilateral-strategy-toward-gaza-will-keep-leading-to-disaster/0000018c-4507-d6bd-a1ad-7fd7ad320000</guid></item><item><title>亚伊尔·戈兰能否利用他的英雄形象打造一个“新鲜、令人兴奋”的以色列左翼？</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-07/ty-article-magazine/.highlight/can-yair-golan-leverage-his-hero-image-to-build-a-fresh-exciting-israeli-left/0000018c-456c-d6bd-a1ad-7ffe83fd0000</link><description>10月7日，这位退役将军展现的英雄气概改变了他的公众形象。现在，他面临着将新获得的人气转化为选票的挑战。在一次深度采访中，戈兰解释了他对加沙战争、与巴勒斯坦人的冲突以及作为以色列左派的态度</description><pubDate>Thu, 07 Dec 2023 21:54:06 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-07/ty-article-magazine/.highlight/can-yair-golan-leverage-his-hero-image-to-build-a-fresh-exciting-israeli-left/0000018c-456c-d6bd-a1ad-7ffe83fd0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列政府允许紧急使用私人安全摄像头</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-07/ty-article/.premium/israeli-government-okays-emergency-access-to-private-security-cams/0000018c-454a-dc19-a3ae-dfee3eaa0000</link><description>新法律允许以色列军队和安全部门在所有者不知情的情况下使用私人安全摄像头。立法者解释说，这是防止敌对摄像头窃听的必要条件，对国家安全至关重要</description><pubDate>Thu, 07 Dec 2023 20:00:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-07/ty-article/.premium/israeli-government-okays-emergency-access-to-private-security-cams/0000018c-454a-dc19-a3ae-dfee3eaa0000</guid></item><item><title>过去24小时内，五名以色列士兵在加沙战斗中丧生</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-07/ty-article/five-israeli-soldiers-killed-in-last-24-hours-in-gaza-fighting/0000018c-456a-dc19-a3ae-dfeefca00000</link><description>以色列军队首先宣布了周三被杀的三名以色列士兵的死亡，随后又公布了周四被杀的另外两名士兵的名字</description><pubDate>Thu, 07 Dec 2023 19:20:02 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-07/ty-article/five-israeli-soldiers-killed-in-last-24-hours-in-gaza-fighting/0000018c-456a-dc19-a3ae-dfeefca00000</guid></item><item><title>以色列领导人悼念在加沙战斗中丧生的战时内阁部长、前以色列国防军司令加迪·艾森科特的儿子</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-07/ty-article/.premium/israeli-leaders-eulogize-son-of-war-cabinet-minister-killed-in-gaza-fighting/0000018c-4533-db03-a7dd-ed77e76c0000</link><description>艾森科特当时正在视察在加沙执行任务的第 162 师，此时他收到了 25 岁的儿子加尔战死的消息。内塔尼亚胡表示哀悼，称“他是一位勇敢的战士和真正的英雄”</description><pubDate>Thu, 07 Dec 2023 18:11:16 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-07/ty-article/.premium/israeli-leaders-eulogize-son-of-war-cabinet-minister-killed-in-gaza-fighting/0000018c-4533-db03-a7dd-ed77e76c0000</guid></item><item><title>很快，拜登将呼吁结束战争。内塔尼亚胡会攻击他</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/haaretz-today/2023-12-07/ty-article/.highlight/soon-biden-will-call-for-the-war-to-end-and-netanyahu-will-attack-him/0000018c-453a-db23-ad9f-6dfaba8b0000</link><description>那么，拜登唯一的问题是，他想在 2024 年什么时候与内塔尼亚胡进行一场战斗</description><pubDate>Thu, 07 Dec 2023 17:44:47 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/haaretz-today/2023-12-07/ty-article/.highlight/soon-biden-will-call-for-the-war-to-end-and-netanyahu-will-attack-him/0000018c-453a-db23-ad9f-6dfaba8b0000</guid></item><item><title>由于人质家人深陷繁文缛节，以色列未能设立机构来帮助他们</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-07/ty-article/.premium/as-hostages-families-drown-in-red-tape-israel-fails-to-set-up-agency-to-help-them/0000018c-44de-db03-a7dd-eddf26600000</link><description>人质家属代表表示，有些家庭支离破碎，得不到任何支持，他们无法坚持下去。</description><pubDate>Thu, 07 Dec 2023 17:15:49 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-07/ty-article/.premium/as-hostages-families-drown-in-red-tape-israel-fails-to-set-up-agency-to-help-them/0000018c-44de-db03-a7dd-eddf26600000</guid></item><item><title>以色列警方试图阻止主要由阿拉伯人组成的左翼哈达什党代表大会</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-07/ty-article/.premium/israeli-police-tries-to-prevent-left-wing-largely-arab-hadash-party-convention/0000018c-4513-d6bd-a1ad-7fd74a250000</link><description>以色列警方声称大会将包括煽动性言论，并威胁举办活动的设施所有者。哈达什领导人表示，议程将包括规划“反对战争继续和政治迫害的政治行动”</description><pubDate>Thu, 07 Dec 2023 17:00:25 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-07/ty-article/.premium/israeli-police-tries-to-prevent-left-wing-largely-arab-hadash-party-convention/0000018c-4513-d6bd-a1ad-7fd74a250000</guid></item><item><title>泰国人在加沙被哈马斯扣为人质：以色列人“受到特别残酷的待遇”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/world-news/asia-and-australia/2023-12-07/ty-article-magazine/thai-man-held-hostage-in-gaza-recalls-beatings-and-bleakness/0000018c-444b-db23-ad9f-6cdb776b0000</link><description>阿努查·安卡尤 (Anucha Angkaew) 与其他几名以色列和泰国人质一起被哈马斯囚禁了 50 天。绑架者对他们拳打脚踢了两天。此后，他们又坚持对以色列人进行两天的殴打，用电线鞭打以色列人。</description><pubDate>Thu, 07 Dec 2023 16:49:55 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/world-news/asia-and-australia/2023-12-07/ty-article-magazine/thai-man-held-hostage-in-gaza-recalls-beatings-and-bleakness/0000018c-444b-db23-ad9f-6cdb776b0000</guid></item><item><title>比利时禁止以色列定居者在西岸实施反巴勒斯坦暴力</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-07/ty-article/.premium/belgium-bans-israeli-settlers-committing-anti-palestinian-violence-in-the-west-bank/0000018c-44b1-df9c-a5ff-f7bb7abd0000</link><description>比利时总理效仿了拜登最近的制裁措施，并表示将推动欧盟效仿。他警告称，自 10 月 7 日哈马斯袭击以来，西岸定居者的暴力行为已达到历史最高水平，“针对平民的暴力行为将会产生后果”</description><pubDate>Thu, 07 Dec 2023 15:57:46 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-07/ty-article/.premium/belgium-bans-israeli-settlers-committing-anti-palestinian-violence-in-the-west-bank/0000018c-44b1-df9c-a5ff-f7bb7abd0000</guid></item><item><title>“好犹太人”与“坏犹太人”：为什么支持巴勒斯坦的抗议活动有问题</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2023-12-07/ty-article-opinion/.premium/good-jew-vs-bad-jew-why-pro-palestine-protests-have-a-problem/0000018c-43d1-db23-ad9f-6bd936010000</link><description>我一直抗议以色列的占领和系统性的反阿拉伯歧视，但我不会加入纽约的亲巴勒斯坦抗议活动。我永远不会接受有毒测试，要求我谴责其他犹太人，也不会与任何将杀害以色列人视为“抵抗”合法化的人一起游行</description><pubDate>Thu, 07 Dec 2023 15:41:23 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2023-12-07/ty-article-opinion/.premium/good-jew-vs-bad-jew-why-pro-palestine-protests-have-a-problem/0000018c-43d1-db23-ad9f-6bd936010000</guid></item></channel></rss>